beginning, containing an area of TWENTY THOUSAND SEVEN HUNDRED SEVENTY SEVEN (20,777) square meters.

All points referred to are indicated on the plan are marked on the ground by Old Points.

Lot 2, H-V-26647

A parcel of land identified as Lot 2, H-V-26647, located in Barangay Basper, Tacloban City. Bounded on the NW. along lines 1-3 by Lot No. 4029; on the E. by Lot No. 5329; on the SE., by Lots No. 5329 and 4025; and on the SW. by Tigbao River. Beginning at a point marked 1 Lot 2 on plan H-V-26647, being N. 0 deg. 48′ E. 298.44 m. from B.L.L.M. 19 Tacloban Cadastre, thence:

