141.26 m. to point. 11;

203.9 to 7 m. to point of

beginning, containing an area of SEVENTY NINE THOUSAND NINE HUNDRED SIXTY SIX (79,966) square meters.

All points referred to are indicated on the plan are marked on the ground as follows: points 6, 7, 8 and 9 by crosses on trees and the rest by Old Points. Bounded on the NW. Along lines 1-3 by Lot 4029, Tacloban Cadastre; along lines 3-5 by Lot 1 of plan H-V-26647; along lines 8-10 by Public land; along lines 10-11 by Lot 4535, Tacloban Cadastre; and along lines 11-1 by Lot 4025, Tacloban Cadastre.

Such part or parts of the area herein declared open for disposition in relation to the provisions of Public Land Act, as amended, which are being used or earmark for public quasi-public purposes shall excluded from such disposition. Existing roads or proposed roads within the area shall conform with provisions of Executive Order No. 113, series of 1995. Likewise, strict compliance to Presidential Decree 856, which outlined the Sanitation Code of the Philippines must be observed.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 7 th day of February, in the year of Our Lord, two thousand and three.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) ALBERTO G. ROMULO Executive Secretary

